{"tid":487960,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇咩牌子空氣加濕機好","createTime":"2017-12-03T08:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T05:48:11.000Z","uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16f2caa207d0af0a72d4b0ea1d04931bf159fa08","tid":487960,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd530285dd87daa916ae24d016954728bf023ea0","tid":487960,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9fa714dab33570cdd8bf874f0742e297d366e9","tid":487960,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"淘寶啦"},{"pid":"344d207ea59612394ebfe45d1c0739d83d0b2033","tid":487960,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"自己放兜水咪得"},{"pid":"723ae5029271808589a2bc5d8c9f0c91e5fbc420","tid":487960,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"so far 得一隻合格，其他全部噴細菌，一係你三日洗一次<br />\n<br />\n自己用緊水貨 dyson AM10 . <br />\n<br />\n支那小米都有款有殺菌，但我唔敢用。始終插電又有水又長開，訓訓下覺爆炸就係咁先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平d 無殺菌功能的話，得番 BONECO 可考慮 ，U7142 可放地有暖噴，水缸有支銀離子棒殺菌叫做好過無，但都要keep住洗缸. <br />\n<br />\n飛利浦果d 係吹張濕紙巾，佢話呢個方法少菌，但其他個filter積係度都會生菌。<br />\n<br />\n總之放濕機呢家野，無殺菌功能真係唔好考慮，一係洗到你傻，一係吹到成屋菌病"}]}